  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867970/extras/2ce3b2e61bbe24a54edf2b2af5b39833.poster.avif?t=1721801653\" width=800 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867970/extras/2ce3b2e61bbe24a54edf2b2af5b39833.webm?t=1721801653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867970/extras/2ce3b2e61bbe24a54edf2b2af5b39833.mp4?t=1721801653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867970/extras/483eca0ec8fbe25b1295dd15e67a2610.avif?t=1721801653\" width=600 height=132 /></span><br><strong>Summer Nightmare is a psychological horror, that shows the life of one of the people, a man who did not love his mother.He was born into a fatherless family, grew up on the streets, and was addicted to gambling.When he found his love, he did not move out from his mother, but brought his beloved to his parents' house.His wife constantly reproached him for living with his mother.One day, his mother died...There were some hitches with the inheritance, but everything was \"miraculously\" resolved ..... His wife still left him when he told her exactly how his mother died, after that, in his life, and some kind of devilry begins to happen at home.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867970/extras/bd72a450cd39fc9de7a0f5abe47d0563.poster.avif?t=1721801653\" width=612 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867970/extras/bd72a450cd39fc9de7a0f5abe47d0563.webm?t=1721801653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867970/extras/bd72a450cd39fc9de7a0f5abe47d0563.mp4?t=1721801653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867970/extras/058ce272eb06b2fd250936a4ca070ff8.avif?t=1721801653\" width=600 height=132 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>A short psychological horror lasting up to 30 minutes.</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Notes</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>No Saves!</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Atmosphere:)</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Unreal Engine 5</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Achievement's</strong></li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867970/extras/1141e1bba24db8b89b432b9fc61cdbeb.poster.avif?t=1721801653\" width=612 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867970/extras/1141e1bba24db8b89b432b9fc61cdbeb.webm?t=1721801653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867970/extras/1141e1bba24db8b89b432b9fc61cdbeb.mp4?t=1721801653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867970/extras/f4cca3aeb4571a764cffe42f98a13094.poster.avif?t=1721801653\" width=612 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867970/extras/f4cca3aeb4571a764cffe42f98a13094.webm?t=1721801653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867970/extras/f4cca3aeb45